r,\nsaid he still believed the animal\nwas alive, although the crew failed\nto hear its barks for the first time\nyesterday.\nThe workers estimated 110 sticks\nof dynamite had been used to\nblast out the earth. Lately they\nhave been using black powder and\nmaking lighter charges because\nthey believed they were nearing\nthe entombed animal.\n\u201cOld Man River.\u2019\u2019 The Murderinjc\nHarpe Brothen and How They Terror\nized the Early Settler* Along the Mia\nniflsippi Revealed bv Capt. Louis\nRoache. the Lant of the Old-Time Mis\nais\u00dfippi River Steamboat Captains in\nAnother Chapter of His Story of Ex\nciting Yean Along the \u201cFather of\nWaters.\u201d A Double Page Feature In\nThe American Weekly, with Sunday\u2019s\n1 Washington Herald-Times. I\nTHE NATIONAL I\nSEVENTH AND H STREETS\n\nAuto Financing\n\u2018Racket\u2019 Revealed\nBALTIMORE. March 1 (1.N.5.).\nState investigators piled up evi\ndence here todaj of \u201clegalized\nracketeering\u201d in numerous cases\nof auto financing, according to\nMaryland Commissioner of Loans\nW. David Tilghman, Jr., who\nplanned to invoke grand jury\naction to break it up. In five J\nmonths of investigation, Tilghman\nsaid his men had uncovered,\n\u201cshocking cases,\u201d II\nTelephone RE publie 1234\nYES, doctor ie\nThe only cough drops containing VITAMIN A are the famous\nI Smith Brothers Cough Drops Recent scientific evidence I\nshows that Vitamin A raises the resistance of the mucous mem\nbranes of the nose and throat to cold and cough infectiona.\n$5.50 Folding Go-Cart, special $2.98\n$19.95 Walnut Finish Cedar Chest $12.88\n$6.95 Maple Finish Play Yard $3.98\n$9.95 Enamel Crib, special $7.88\n$22.95 3-Piece Case Fiber Suite $17.88 m\n$15.95 100-Piece Set of Dishes $9.95\n$2.59 Mahogany and Chrome Cocktail\nSmoker $1.49 H\n$26.95 Studio, with innerspring mattress. $14.88\n$42.50 Studio with arms and back $29.85\n$39.95 Studio in fine Friezette $27.60\n$54.95 Studio with arms and back $34.95 N\n$49.95 Daventw